description:
In this course we touch on a broad range of SEO subjects to give you some quick tactical wins as well as an understanding some of the deeper SEO concepts and strategies. This course provides digestible information for all levels of knowledge, from users just beginning to learn SEO to advanced SEOs.

If you like what you see here feel free to stay up to date on current information at our blog: Moz Blog

Also if you would like to take a free trial of our product sign up here: Moz Analytics Free Trial!
title: Advanced SEO: Tactics and Strategy
